&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif; font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Interested in joining a growing company where you will work with talented colleagues, enhance a supportive and energetic culture, and be part of the climate solution? At Energy Solutions, we focus on the big impacts. And we believe that market-based programs can be a powerful force to deliver large-scale energy, carbon, and water-use savings. Since 1995, we’ve harnessed that power to offer proven, performance-based solutions for our utility, government, and institutional customers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;&quot;&gt;Energy Solutions is currently seeking a full-time &lt;strong&gt;Learning &amp;amp; Development Manager (L&amp;amp;D) &lt;/strong&gt;to join our People and Culture Department. As Manager of Learning &amp;amp; Development, you’ll supervise instructional designers and other learning and development team members to design and develop training—from new hire onboarding to ongoing professional development. You’ll support business strategy and execution of engaging, instructionally sound learning experiences rooted in adult learning principles, ensuring every program impacts the culture at ES.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
