&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif; font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif; font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Execute assigned program workflows (e.g., claim intake, completeness review, eligibility verification within guidelines) to support service levels and processing timelines.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif; font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif; font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Review, validate, and process applications and claims in accordance with program rules, eligibility criteria, and SOPs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
